.\" Man page for appicon
.TH APPICON 1 "July 2026" "appicon" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
appicon \- resolve desktop and brand icons to local file paths
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B appicon
\fIcommand\fR [\fIoptions\fR] [\fIargs\fR...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B appicon
looks up an application or brand icon and prints a local filesystem path.
Consumers such as Waybar, Rofi, and scripts can use the path without embedding
remote download logic.
.PP
Default resolve order: file, overrides.json, FreeDesktop icon theme / .desktop
(including Flatpak, Snap, and Steam heuristics), then SVGL. Customize the full
pipeline (including opt-in CDN/github/glyph stages and local packs) via
sources.json. See docs/sources.md and docs/packs.md. A miss exits with status 1
unless a glyph stage is reached.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B resolve [\-\-json] [\-\-offline] [\-\-local] [\-\-order \fITYPES\fR] [\-\-format svg|png] [\-\-size N] [\-\-theme dark|light] \fIquery\fR
Resolve \fIquery\fR and print the absolute path (or JSON with \-\-json).
\-\-order is a comma-separated list of stage types (same semantics as sources.json).
When a daemon socket is present, dial it unless \-\-local or APPICON_NO_DAEMON is set.
.TP
.B prefetch \fIquery\fR...
Warm the cache for one or more queries (same effective order as resolve).
.TP
.B cache path|clear|stats|prune
Inspect or manage the on-disk cache under $XDG_CACHE_HOME/appicon.
.TP
.B override list|get|set|rm|path [\-\-json]
Manage $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/appicon/overrides.json query remaps (long-tail aliases).
.TP
.B sources list|path [\-\-json]
Show effective resolve stage order or the sources.json path.
.TP
.B pack list|path|add|install|update [\-\-json] ...
Manage local icon packs (add directory, install recipes or git/.tar.gz URLs,
update clones, or install from \-\-from-bundle).
.TP
.B daemon [\-\-socket \fIpath\fR]
Run the optional unix-socket resolve daemon (or under systemd socket activation).
.TP
.B mcp
Run a stdio MCP server for coding agents (tools: resolve, prefetch, sources_*,
pack_*, override_*, cache_*, version). Prefer MCP tools over shelling the CLI when connected.
.TP
.B completion bash|zsh|fish
Print a shell completion script to stdout.
.TP
.B man
Print this man page (troff) to stdout.
.TP
.B version
Print the version string.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B XDG_CACHE_HOME
Cache root parent (default ~/.cache). Assets live in $XDG_CACHE_HOME/appicon.
.TP
.B XDG_CONFIG_HOME
Config parent (default ~/.config). Reads appicon/overrides.json and sources.json.
.TP
.B XDG_DATA_HOME
Data parent (default ~/.local/share). Packs default under appicon/packs/.
.TP
.B APPICON_THEME
Default dark|light preference when \-\-theme is omitted.
.TP
.B APPICON_ICON_THEME
Override FreeDesktop icon theme name.
.TP
.B APPICON_SOCKET
Override daemon socket path (default $XDG_RUNTIME_DIR/appicon.sock).
.TP
.B APPICON_NO_DAEMON
When set, resolve never dials the daemon socket.
.TP
.B APPICON_OFFLINE
When set, skip network (same as resolve \-\-offline); pack install/update refuse.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/appicon/overrides.json
Query remaps (e.g. WM class to catalog name).
.TP
.I $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/appicon/sources.json
Ordered resolve stages (file, overrides, xdg, pack, svgl, opt-in remotes, glyph).
.TP
.I $XDG_DATA_HOME/appicon/packs/
Recommended local pack root.
.TP
.I $XDG_CACHE_HOME/appicon/
Downloaded SVGs, CDN/github assets, glyph SVGs, and rasterized PNGs.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success.
.TP
.B 1
Not found (supported miss for consumers).
.TP
.B 2
Usage or configuration error.
.SH SEE ALSO
docs/sources.md, docs/packs.md, docs/consumer-contract.md
